firebase-ai.author: emilypgoogle
firebase-ai.message:
Add NotConfiguredException with a better error message than provided by the server. (#7233)

The previous error text "genai config not found" is ambiguous and as a
generic ServerException did not provide documentation for resolutions.

firebase-ai.author: Ryan Wilson
firebase-ai.message:
Temporarily remove CHANGELOG entry (#7228)

The backend won't be published until sometime next week, removing this
until it's ready. No changes to the code are necessary as there are no
public API changes and it'll still hit a runtime error.

firebase-perf.author: Tejas Deshpande
firebase-perf.message:
Refactor RCM fetch random delay to not depend on FirebaseApp initialization. (#7214)

This should help address the issue where there could be a deadlock if
`FirebaseApp` is still being initialized.

See https://github.com/firebase/firebase-android-sdk/issues/4831
